    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "This makes me homesick. \ud83c\udf35 \u2665\ufe0f\n\n\nJorge Torres (@JorgeTWeather)\n\nPhoenix is about to experience something that has never happened in March.\n\n102\u00b0 by Wednesday.\n\n105\u00b0 by Thursday. \n\nSome daily records could shatter by 10 degrees \ud83c\udf21\ufe0f\n\n105\u00b0 would also tie the hottest temperature ever recorded in APRIL. \n\nIt\u2019s only March.\n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/JorgeTWeather/status/2032434050477265224#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2032493483680821757",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T16:26:23+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "There have now been four jihadist attacks on the US homeland in the last two weeks and one at the school I took my kids to see Disney on Ice at.\n\nDon\u2019t try and gaslight me Muslim extemism isn\u2019t a full blown crisis in this country.",
